OL,3,CUK Government told it 'could have gone
OL,4,Cfurther' on North Sea windfall tax
OL,6,FThe UK Government "could have gone
OL,7,Ffurther" with its plans to reform the
OL,8,Fwindfall tax on oil and gas companies,
OL,9,Fthe chairwoman of a Westminster
OL,10,Fcommittee has insisted.
OL,12,FIn response to a report from MPs on
OL,13,Fthe Scottish Affairs Committee,
OL,14,Fministers made clear they had set a
OL,15,F"clear path" for the measure,
OL,16,Fofficially called the energy profits
OL,17,Flevy (EPL), to end by March 2030 "at
OL,18,Fthe latest".
