OL,3,CUK Government told it 'could have gone
OL,4,Cfurther' on North Sea windfall tax
OL,6,FThe levy, currently set at 38%, has
OL,7,Fbeen blamed by leading figures in the
OL,8,Fsector for job losses, with the
OL,9,Fcommittee report in October 2025
OL,10,Fstating that a "lack of clarity" on
OL,11,Fthe fiscal regime in the North Sea
OL,12,Fafter the end of this decade had
OL,13,F"created uncertainty for industry".
OL,15,FIn its response the UK Government said
OL,16,Fit had "set a clear path for the
OL,17,Fenergy profits levy to end by March
OL,18,F2030 at the latest".
