OL,3,CUK Government told it 'could have gone
OL,4,Cfurther' on North Sea windfall tax
OL,6,FBut it also stressed that cash raised
OL,7,Fby it contributed to the drive
OL,8,F"towards cleaner energy" and also
OL,9,Fhelped support "the funding of wider
OL,10,Fpublic services".
OL,12,FScottish Affairs Committee chairwoman
OL,13,FPatricia Ferguson said she welcomed
OL,14,Fthe "reaffirmation of plans to
OL,15,Fintroduce a reformed windfall tax
OL,16,Fmechanism after 2030", adding that
OL,17,Fthis "is a positive step".
