OL,3,CUK Government told it 'could have gone
OL,4,Cfurther' on North Sea windfall tax
OL,6,FMs Ferguson said it was "encouraging"
OL,7,Fthat ministers had made "clear
OL,8,Fcommitments and plans to create more
OL,9,Fsecure clean energy jobs".
OL,11,FBut she insisted: "The proof, of
OL,12,Fcourse, will be in the delivery. We've
OL,13,Fyet to see concrete evidence of
OL,14,Fdelivery and implementation of these
OL,15,Finitiatives."
OL,17,FMPs on the committee will "continue to
OL,18,Fmonitor the UK Government's progress
OL,19,Fclosely to ensure it delivers for
OL,20,FScottish workers", she vowed.
