OL,6,FShe spoke out in the wake of the UK
OL,7,FGovernment's response to the
OL,8,Fcommittee's report, which had warned
OL,9,Fthat until clean energy jobs can be
OL,10,Fcreated at the scale needed to match
OL,11,Fjob losses in fossil fuels, the UK
OL,12,FGovernment "should avoid accelerating
OL,13,Fthe decline of North Sea oil and gas
OL,14,Fproduction".
OL,16,FMs Ferguson recalled: "Our report
OL,17,Fraised serious concerns that clean
OL,18,Fenergy jobs aren't being created at
OL,19,Fthe pace or scale needed to keep up
OL,20,Fwith job losses in the North Sea oil
OL,21,Fand gas sector.
