OL,6,F"Whilst the UK Government didn't
OL,7,Facknowledge this view in their
OL,8,Fresponse, it is encouraging to see
OL,9,Fclear commitments and plans to create
OL,10,Fmore secure clean energy jobs."
OL,12,FThe Government response however said
OL,13,Fthat the clean energy jobs plan it had
OL,14,Fpublished in October last year was a
OL,15,F"major step forward in supporting the
OL,16,Fclean energy transition".
